Find threshold for outliers triming based on inter quartile range.

Source: R/IqrThreshold.R
IqrThreshold.Rd

Find threshold for outliers triming based on inter quartile range.

Arguments

x.num

<numeric>: numeric vector.

iqrFactor.num

<numeric>: inter quartile range factor. (Default 1.5)

bounds.chr

<character>: bounds to return, "lower", "upper" or "both". (Default "both")

Value

numerical vector of minmal and/or maximal thresholds values for outliers triming.

Details

IqrThreshold

Examples

set.seed(1111)
x.num <- rnorm(1000)
x.num <- sort(x.num)
